('computer-science:2-2-3b-arrays:match:fd660043', 'computer-science', 'computer-science:2-2-3b-arrays', '2.2.3b Arrays', 'match', 'mcq', 1, '{"question": "Which definition matches the key term “array scores[5]”?", "options": ["An array whose size is fixed once declared and cannot grow or shrink", "A single value stored at one position (index) within an array", "Refers to the top-left cell of a 2D array", "Declares a static, 0-indexed 1D array with 5 elements (indices 0 to 4)"]}'::jsonb, '{"answer": 3, "explain": "“array scores[5]” means: Declares a static, 0-indexed 1D array with 5 elements (indices 0 to 4)"}'::jsonb),
